    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountInfo.Request, AuxToken.Request, IncomingTransferAccept.Request, IncomingTransferReject.Request, InstanceId.Request, OperationDetails.Request, OperationHistory.Request, ProcessExternalPayment.Request, ProcessPayment.Request, RequestExternalPayment.Request, RequestPayment.Request, Token.Request, Token.Revoke

    public abstract class FirstApiRequest<T>
extends BaseApiRequest<T>

    Base implementation of ApiRequest for API v1. Parses only JSON responses otherwise InvalidRequestException is thrown.

    If server returns HTTP status code 200 (Ok), 202 (Accepted) or 400 (Bad request) then this object will try to parse body of a response

    If server returns HTTP status code 401 (Unauthorized) then InvalidTokenException is thrown.

    If server returns HTTP status code 403 (Forbidden) then InsufficientScopeException is thrown.

    In other cases IOException is thrown

    .
